data.description: Back on the market! It's your chance to make this nice home your home in Paradise. New & better price for the spacious home with $5,000.00 towards closing costs in the desirable Olino at Mehana community! This bright contemporary 3 bedroom/2 bath townhouse features the perfect blend of comfort & style: open floor plan with vinyl/carpet flooring, dark cherry cabinets with Corian counters, new upgraded "Samsung" appliances, lots of closets & plenty of space. The primary bedroom is private, spacious & with walk-in closet. The space is filled with natural light, thanks to large windows that offer picturesque views of park & community. Enjoy park views from your balcony or yard, which is perfect for entertainment or relaxation. Pet friendly community. Enjoy the community swimming pool, Mehana gym, jogging/walking paths & multiple playgrounds & parks. Conveniently close to major shopping centers & famous Ko Olina lagoons. Don't miss out on your dream home in the vibrant community of Kapolei! One or more photos were enhanced. The rooms are virtually staged.
